  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uber Destruction is packed with awesome roguelike elements. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Just how much action are we talking?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355200/extras/c18a17a781ad4ac8c86a0c2f6e8b29c6.webp?t=1739845049\" width=612 height=24 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355200/extras/9dbc985996640f6d9cb6f8bfed8a87ba.poster.avif?t=1739845049\" width=600 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355200/extras/9dbc985996640f6d9cb6f8bfed8a87ba.webm?t=1739845049\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><strong>Find unique weapons and items from all sorts of chests.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355200/extras/e226e19a4a8f32452b6280c723ff2e52.poster.avif?t=1739845049\" width=600 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355200/extras/e226e19a4a8f32452b6280c723ff2e52.webm?t=1739845049\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><strong>Plenty of ways to take down your foes!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355200/extras/0ae3d33fdb4d513c367c1a9aad45a5a1.apng?t=1739845049\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355200/extras/0ae3d33fdb4d513c367c1a9aad45a5a1.poster.avif?t=1739845049\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=240 /></picture></span><strong>Earn and save your shards to purchase different upgrades.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Online Multiplayer & local co-op mode</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlockable characters</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Chests and shops</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Variety of levels</strong> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Wicked bosses</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tons of enemies</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Insane weapons</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Powerful items</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bumpin' soundtrack</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Silly references</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>And DESTRUCTION!</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355200/extras/c18a17a781ad4ac8c86a0c2f6e8b29c6.webp?t=1739845049\" width=612 height=24 /></span></p>",
